data.Name: SVDDEN DEATH
data.Bio: a rising San Jose-born/LA-based talent, started Svdden Death in March 2015 He’s remixed his name. He’s had two tracks on Buygore’s latest Fresh Blood compilation. He’s gigging heavily, including key shows with the consistently on-point Savage Society crew and support for the unstoppable Dion Timmer. Read more on Last.fm
